{"tid":1808042,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"法定假返工有另外出糧，仲駛唔駛補假?","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:01:09.000Z","uid":3185,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5244955be642b5e05f6f4331df7d0284244a47","tid":1808042,"uid":3185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"有冇勞工法例高手?<br />\n如果我1月1日有返工，公司有另外出糧，咁仲需唔需要補假?<br />\n仲要如果我12月31號返到1月1日先收工，係當我開ot定係法定假返工?"},{"pid":"9bcc0c600dba88092305b90c58dc8f89ee231f5d","tid":1808042,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"有啲假係冇得折現, 一定要補假...<br />\n包唔包1月1日就唔知"},{"pid":"c37d8a3f73a12cda7b6a0aa816aab8500bed7835","tid":1808042,"uid":3185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bcc0c600dba88092305b90c58dc8f89ee231f5d","tid":1808042,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"有啲假係冇得折現, 一定要補假...<br />\n包唔包1月1日就唔知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"1月1日係法定假，照睇係一定要放，<br />\n但係我老細又話有補水就唔駛補假，我同佢係到拗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d8348e65266178cb51345dd98427f35fc971e8","tid":1808042,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37d8a3f73a12cda7b6a0aa816aab8500bed7835","tid":1808042,"uid":3185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bcc0c600dba88092305b90c58dc8f89ee231f5d","tid":1808042,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"有啲假係冇得折現, 一定要補假...<br />\n包唔包1月1日就唔知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"1月1日係法定假，照睇係一定要放，<br />\n但係我老細又話有補水就唔駛補假，我同佢係到拗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"睇合約，通常呢啲日子出多兩三倍人工"},{"pid":"3f74079d9f4e1a4e82803c769668f8701e9d8a8d","tid":1808042,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c37d8a3f73a12cda7b6a0aa816aab8500bed7835","tid":1808042,"uid":3185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bcc0c600dba88092305b90c58dc8f89ee231f5d","tid":1808042,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"有啲假係冇得折現, 一定要補假...<br />\n包唔包1月1日就唔知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"1月1日係法定假，照睇係一定要放，<br />\n但係我老細又話有補水就唔駛補假，我同佢係到拗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"根據勞工法例，老闆有權要求員工在法定假日工作，只須在事前至少48小時通知員工，並在該法定假日前或後60天內安排另訂假日給員工便可。如勞資雙方同意，老闆可在法定假日或另訂假日的30天內安排代替假日給員工。在這些情況下，勞工處建議老闆應為員工所發放的另訂假日或代替假日保存清楚的記錄，避免不必要的紛爭。"},{"pid":"ee8c2b95b498e42f7aad8824a2bbb7bf4d6eac82","tid":1808042,"uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"老闆不得以任何形式的款項代替發放法定假日給僱員，即是只能作出補假安排，不能補錢。僱主如違反這項規定，可被檢控，一經定罪，可被罰款港幣五萬元。"},{"pid":"95995b582b1039a660535e99b7c28868ceaeb1d4","tid":1808042,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/articles/%E7%B4%85%E6%97%A5%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5-%E8%A3%9C%E9%8C%A2%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E8%A3%9C%E5%81%87-%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E9%80%99%E6%A8%A3%E5%81%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fen-hk%2Farticles%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%258C%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2581%2587-%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2583%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E5%2581%259A%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=0ebf3d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/articles/%E7%B4%85%E6%97%A5%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5-%E8%A3%9C%E9%8C%A2%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E8%A3%9C%E5%81%87-%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%9